snippet.title: Norman's Great Illusion Release Trailer
snippet.description:
"Norman's Great Illusion" is a 2D pixel art visual novel in which you have to live a year as an engineer at the factory in the face of rising social tensions. Make difficult decisions, but keep in mind: you will have to pay for each choice
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/463510/Normans_Great_Illusion
